description: Summer is still in full swing here in the Czech Republic. People are enjoying warm weather and so do I. Once again, I went hunting near water. There I accidentally bumped into my old friend Enzo. We had some fun a few years ago so I sat down for a little chat. It turned out he was almost broke and definitely willing to pimp his horny friends for my pleasure. Well, I´d be crazy to pass such an opportunity. It took a few calls but eventually we were joined by Lukas. Enzo and I had a simple plan. We would just destroy the Lukas much to his delight. We also tried local restroom only to find out that three people can barely fit inside. So I took my slutty friends into a nearby forest. There poor Honza found out how hard it is to satisfy two hungry cocks.
title: Czech Hunter 368
